{"tid":2310478,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"賣一部虧1100元：索尼PS5居然還要降價","createTime":"2020-12-03T09:41:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-03T09:50:51.000Z","uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"985c1ea658d1179d3dbc895c5c36d71a4db2a8c8","tid":2310478,"uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T09:41:51.000Z","msg":"日前，一家東南亞的電商分析機構發布報告，預計索尼PS5的價格將在明年逐步下滑。明年5月數字版降至379美元，光驅版降至469美元。<br />\n<br />\n  有購買意向的用戶如果等到明年Q3，那麼數字版降至345美元（約合2200元），光驅版降至432美元，降幅分別達到了54美元和67美元（約合439元）。<br />\n<br />\n  <img src=\"https://nimg.ws.126.net/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fcrawl.ws.126.net%2F1190397ca92d61aca9ab1e0f01b4f0b2.jpg&amp;thumbnail=650x2147483647&amp;quality=80&amp;type=jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnimg.ws.126.net%2F%3Furl%3Dhttp%253A%252F%252Fcrawl.ws.126.net%252F1190397ca92d61aca9ab1e0f01b4f0b2.jpg%26thumbnail%3D650x2147483647%26quality%3D80%26type%3Djpg&h=b7d46ffb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n  在圖表中，同樣399美元發售的PS4 Pro就交出了類似的降價&ldquo;成績單&rdquo;。<br />\n<br />\n  其實業內人士之前透露，索尼PS5目前硬件上是虧錢的。據說現在賣一台虧170美元（約合1115元），如果這麼快就給經銷商繼續讓利，豈不是虧得更多了？"},{"pid":"7884baa710ead196e87db4ce34db162e40eaa71a","tid":2310478,"uid":344625,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T09:43:21.000Z","msg":"不如話賣一部蝕99999啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f54a4ebbe0894cc8061546de1263df227315ddc","tid":2310478,"uid":330057,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T09:44:49.000Z","msg":"索尼滔天大罪<br />\n索尼都係想大家有機打<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff87a5650a6f84adb6d9a35a35c3ff0c2a31ded0","tid":2310478,"uid":81698,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T09:44:58.000Z","msg":"屌下年個成本唔通又一樣咩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"adefe88355a364c7c071c44c3969ae57fc268ac1","tid":2310478,"uid":38218,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTim